@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lpksob(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin((v0 * (v1 + 0.46 * v0 + 0.11)))
    v0 = (0.64 + wp.abs((tmp + 0.51 + v2 + 0.83)))
    v0 = wp.cos((v1 / (v0 + 0.75 / v2 + 0.02)))
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
